lead_paragraph: In January 2007, mega-recruit Jimmy Clausen enrolled at Notre Dame, bypassing a final semester of high school to partake in spring practice with the Fighting Irish and get a jump on becoming the starting quarterback.

headline.print_headline: Fast Track: Early Enrollment Now Common in College Football
headline.main: Fast Track: Early Enrollment Now Common in College Football
